name.zh_CN: 全球速卖通数据导出工具

short.am,ar,bg,bn,ca,cs,da,de,el,en,en_AU,en_G: Export data from AliExpress™ to .csv file.
short.zh_CN: 从全球速卖通导出数据为csv文件

long.am,ar,bn,ca,cs,da,de,el,en,en_AU,en_GB,e:
Easily export detailed product and order information from AliExpress directly to a CSV file.  Extract valuable data such as product images, titles, prices, shipping costs, and category names with  a few clicks

How It Works
● Install the Extension: Add the FindNiche - AliExpress Data Exporter to your Chrome browser.
● Navigate to AliExpress: Go to AliExpress.com and browse the products or your order list.
● Export data: Click the extension icon and the extension will generate a CSV file
